{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "We travelled to Dachau for three days and three nights in cattle cars, without any food, without any water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "We arrived in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "We came to the [GERMAN], which is the square of assembly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "We were lined up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "And they put out kettles with boiled cabbage and potatoes and peels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "And they were just about to open up and start feeding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "We could smell the cabbage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "There was 2,000 people lined up, hungry, like animals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "And the alarm went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "There was an air raid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "And we were told to go into ditches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "And we all had to disperse into the ditches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "And the air raid lasted quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "While we were sitting there, we were praying for the American planes to bomb us and bomb our tormentors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "But all they did drop leaflets, to tell us that they knew we are there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 144,
      "text": "They bombed the industrial facilities not far outside Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 145,
      "text": "Some of the inmates could not contain themselves, because they were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 146,
      "text": "And they ran out during the air raid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 147,
      "text": "They ran out, and opened up the kettles and started grabbing the food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 148,
      "text": "And the SS, from the towers, machine gunned them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 149,
      "text": "So later on when we lined up to eat, we were stepping over the bodies of our dead comrades who could not control their hunger.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 150,
      "text": "We stayed in Dachau for several weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 151,
      "text": "I think on the second week of our presence over there, we were told that we'll have to go to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 152,
      "text": "We will be given new numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 153,
      "text": "We're going to change our clothes, we're going to be given new numbers, and we're going to go to another camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 154,
      "text": "While we were in Poland, in the camps, each of us had some personal belongings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 155,
      "text": "We used to hide them and keep them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
